</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3f5ed2e5b510d62fe2d945e30bd036b22300708","tid":1913191,"uid":196075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"有無d正經d既分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼都欺凌阿 呃蝦條阿果d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d8e13cf60d90a10213f6a2228e343189a83e27","tid":1913191,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"用個zip袋入住支粉筆顏成粉審落同學個書包入面"},{"pid":"08927541bc462c03e3d38539a7ccc175e116f72f","tid":1913191,"uid":196075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20d8e13cf60d90a10213f6a2228e343189a83e27","tid":1913191,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"用個zip袋入住支粉筆顏成粉審落同學個書包入面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"佢最後知唔知係你做 有無嬲你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01c3ac495417649b55b327f0623094784c894ed","tid":1913191,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"係巴士成日要ex唅"},{"pid":"d65ebbbb5816780021f8c90a3deb7f5fc4a86321","tid":1913191,"uid":85020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"打機果陣扮女仔呃左好多台仔既裝備<br />\n咁多年黎一直都放唔低"},{"pid":"e3d8154181ad77dad723deeb9c79dea3aa977e0e","tid":1913191,"uid":15387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202